-- MOVES-Kevin Addison joins Brooks Macdonald Funds as head of sales
-- By Anet Josline Pinto in Bangalore
-- Thu Oct 09, 2014 07:03AM EDT
-- None



Oct 9 (Reuters) - Brooks Macdonald Funds Ltd (BMF), the fund management arm of Brooks Macdonald Group Plc <BRK.L>, named Kevin Addison as head of sales.

BMF said Addison, who has over 26 years of experience, joins from SEI Investments Co <SEIC.O>, where he was managing director and head of UK and European asset management distribution.